transfers or taxis. Parking facilities are available for up to 550 vehicles outside the terminal building.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category-inline|Dalaman International Airport}}\n*{{Official|http://en.yda.aero/}}\n*{{WAD|LTBS|source=[[DAFIF]]}}\n*{{GCM|LTBS|source=DAFIF}}\n*{{NWS-current|LTBS}}\n*{{ASN|DLM}}\n\n{{Portalbar|Turkey|Aviation}}\n{{Airports in Turkey}}\n\n]\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Airports in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Mu\u011fla Province]]\n[[Category:Transport in Mu\u011fla Province]]\n[[Category:[https://www.holidayhoppa.com/airport/dalaman-airport-transfers Transport from Dalaman Airport]]\n", "name_user": "95.10.5.240", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eGround Transport)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dalaman_Airport"}
